   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Sourcing Events (Portal)</uicontrol> tab.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the appropriate sourcing event and click <uicontrol>View</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206029/69206093.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Award</uicontrol> tab and you can view the details of your Award winning deal.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206029/69206104.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To view more details like product group, sub-group, items, and price-modifiers of your awarded deal, click <uicontrol>View More</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206029/69206113.png"/>
               </fig>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206029/69206139.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To go back to the Sourcing Event page, click the <uicontrol>Back to Sourcing Event </uicontrol>link.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
